description:
FlexibleQoSFunction: Table storing flexible QoS function parameters for specific cells at a given time, including identifiers, data type, and version information.
dateTime: Timestamp of the QoS function configuration.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located (e.g., NR cell in Balikpapan).
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (likely a copy of CellId).
Id3: An additional, unspecified identifier.
vsDataType: Type of data representing the flexible QoS function.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format used.
FlexibleQoSFunction.flexibleQoSFunctionId: Unique identifier of the flexible QoS function configuration.
queries: Show me all FlexibleQoSFunction entries for CellId 'XYZ123' where vsDataType is 'LTE'.
What is the vsDataFormatVersion for FlexibleQoSFunction configurations in the 'Jakarta' Area_Name after 2023-10-26?
Retrieve all FlexibleQoSFunction parameters where flexibleQoSFunctionId is 'FQF-456' and dateTime is between '2023-10-27 00:00:00' and '2023-10-27 23:59:59'.
Find all discrepancies between CellId and Id2 in the FlexibleQoSFunction table.
How many unique flexibleQoSFunctionId entries exist for each Area_Name in the FlexibleQoSFunction table?
